then 3 tables in that database are

   blog

		Name	Type	Collation	Attributes	Null	Default	Comments	Extra	Action
	1	blog_id Primary	int(11)			No	None		AUTO_INCREMENT	Change Change	Drop Drop	
	2	blog_title	varchar(255)	utf8mb4_general_ci		No	None			Change Change	Drop Drop	
	3	blog_body	varchar(255)	utf8mb4_general_ci		No	None			Change Change	Drop Drop	
	4	blog_image	varchar(255)	utf8mb4_general_ci		No	None			Change Change	Drop Drop	
	5	category	int(11)			No	None			Change Change	Drop Drop	
	6	author_id	int(11)			No	None			Change Change	Drop Drop	
	7	publish_date	timestamp			No	current_timestamp()			Change Change	Drop Drop

